We design Flint to be portable.


== Debian jessie/stretch/sid

We do not have a Debian package (.deb) for Flint yet.
Before building Flint, you will want to install prerequisite Debian packages
as follows:
$ sudo apt-get install gcc g++ autoconf automake libtool bison flex openjdk-7-jdk \
    pkgconf zlib1g-dev


== Fedora 21

Install necessary tools for building and installing Flint with:
$ sudo yum install gcc gcc-c++ autoconf automake libtool bison flex java-1.7.0-openjdk \
    wget zlib-devel


== Ubuntu 14.04.1 LTS (Trusty Tahr)

All you have to do for installing necessary tools is:
$ sudo apt-get install g++ autoconf automake libtool bison flex openjdk-7-jdk


